de.gnwi.mfsim.model.particle

Class StandardParticleInteractionData

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.gnwi.mfsim.model.particle.StandardParticleInteractionData

  • public final class StandardParticleInteractionData
extends java.lang.Object
    Singleton that manages data for particles and particle-particle interactions. NOTE: If possible this singleton also initialises AminoAcids singleton.
    Author:
    Achim Zielesny
